                <h1>Do Background Checks Process on Weekends?</h1>
                <p>Background checks typically do not process on weekends. Most employers and agencies operate during standard business hours, meaning requests made on weekends are often queued until the following business day. This delay can affect the hiring timeline, so it's essential for candidates to be aware of potential wait times.</p>
